Package: slrmodel
Type: Package
Title: slrmodel is a package for fitting simple linear regression model to given predictor variable and response variable.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Leyuan Qian
Maintainer: Leyuan Qian <lyqian@umich.edu>
Description: The slrmodel package uses the method of least squares to find coefficients of the best fitting line for the given data and examine the overall fitness of the line.
